@dev Optional enumeration extension for ERC-721 non-fungible token standard.
 See https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/blob/master/EIPS/eip-721.md.

devdoc.details: Optional enumeration extension for ERC-721 non-fungible token standard. See https://github.com/ethereum/EIPs/blob/master/EIPS/eip-721.md.

tokenByIndex(uint256).details: Returns the token identifier for the `_index`th NFT. Sort order is not specified.

tokenOfOwnerByIndex(address,uint256).details: Returns the token identifier for the `_index`th NFT assigned to `_owner`. Sort order is not specified. It throws if `_index` >= `balanceOf(_owner)` or if `_owner` is the zero address, representing invalid NFTs.

params._owner: An address where we are interested in NFTs owned by them.

totalSupply().details: Returns a count of valid NFTs tracked by this contract, where each one of them has an assigned and queryable owner not equal to the zero address.
